    <!-- Breadcrumb Section Begin -->
    <section class="breadcrumb-option">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <div class="breadcrumb__text">
                        <h4>Cancellation & Refund Policy</h4>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Breadcrumb Section End -->
    <section class="banner spad" style="/*! padding: 0; */padding: 3rem 3rem 3rem 3rem;">
        <div class="relative flex w-[calc(100%-50px)] flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3 lg:w-[calc(100%-115px)]">
            <div class="flex flex-grow flex-col gap-3">
                <div class="min-h-[20px] flex flex-col items-start gap-4 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">
                    <div class="markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light">

                        <p>Thank you for shopping with IndiMart. We strive to provide you with the best online shopping
                            experience and want to ensure that you are completely satisfied with your purchase. In the
                            event that you need to cancel an order or request a refund, please review our Cancellation
                            &amp; Refund Policy outlined below.</p>
                        <ol>
                            <li>
                                <p>Cancellation Policy: 1.1 Order Cancellation by the Customer: If you wish to cancel
                                    your order, please contact our customer support team as soon as possible. We accept
                                    cancellation requests within 24 hours of placing the order. After 24 hours, the
                                    cancellation request may not be possible due to order processing and shipping
                                    preparations.</p>
                                <p>1.2 Order Cancellation by IndiMart: IndiMart reserves the right to cancel an order
                                    under certain circumstances, including but not limited to: - Unavailability of the
                                    product or stock. - Inaccurate pricing or product information. - Fraudulent or
                                    suspicious transactions. - Non-compliance with our Terms of Service. In such cases,
                                    we will notify you of the cancellation and provide a full refund of the order
                                    amount.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p>Refund Policy: 2.1 Eligibility for Refunds: We offer refunds in the following
                                    scenarios: - Order cancellation requested within the stipulated time frame. -
                                    Receipt of damaged, defective, or incorrect products.</p>
                                <p>2.2 Refund Process: To initiate a refund, please contact our customer support team
                                    with relevant details such as order number, product information, and reason for the
                                    refund request. Our team will guide you through the refund process and assist with
                                    any required documentation. Refunds will be processed using the same payment method
                                    used for the original purchase. Please note that refund processing times may vary
                                    depending on the payment gateway and financial institution involved.</p>
                                <p>2.3 Non-Refundable Items and Services: The following items and services are
                                    non-refundable: - Digital products or downloadable content once accessed or
                                    downloaded. - Products with hygiene concerns (e.g., personal care items, intimate
                                    apparel). - Perishable goods such as food, flowers, or custom-made items. - Services
                                    that have already been provided or consumed.</p>
                                <p>2.4 Return Shipping: In the case of eligible returns or exchanges, IndiMart will
                                    provide return shipping instructions and, if applicable, cover the return shipping
                                    costs. Please follow the provided instructions to ensure a smooth return process.
                                </p>
                            </li>

                        </ol>
                        <p>Please note that this Cancellation &amp; Refund Policy is subject to change at our
                            discretion. It is advisable to review this policy periodically for any updates or revisions.
                        </p>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

